{
  "name": "Concentration Aid",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/alchemy.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may choose for your poison to not cause fatigue instantly, but instead to enhance the concentration of those subjected to it (this talent cannot be used with a contact or inhaled poison). Those who are under the effects of this poison gain a +3 alchemical bonus to their concentration checks, but suffer an equivalent penalty to Perception checks for 1 minute. At the end of this talent&#8217;s duration, the creature must succeed at a Fortitude save or be fatigued for 10 minutes. If you possess at least 10 ranks in Craft (alchemy), this bonus increases by +2. A creature cannot benefit from a concentration aid more than once per hour.</p>\n",
